de.upb.pcm.prm

Interface PCMModelElementMeasurement

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, UniqueElement
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ResourceContainerMeasurement
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    PCMModelElementMeasurementImpl, ResourceContainerMeasurementImpl

    public interface PCMModelElementMeasurement
extends UniqueElement
    A representation of the model object ' PCM Model Element Measurement'. Measurement for a pcm model element.

    The following features are supported:

    • Pcm Model Element
    • Measurement Specification
    • Measurement Value

    See Also:
    PrmPackage.getPCMModelElementMeasurement()
